- "Stands tallest among its peers" means having the highest annotation-to-entry ratio.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT e.entry_id) AS total_entries
FROM entries e
INNER JOIN annotations a ON e.entry_id = a.entry_id;

external_knowledge:
